---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import EmailLink from '../components/EmailLink.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for No Lock-In Printer, including hosting, advertising disclosures, affiliate links, and third-party services."
>
  <article class="article">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--amber);">Privacy policy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">This policy distinguishes the site's current static operation from services that may be added only after their configuration and disclosures are complete.</p>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        The current site is a static website. We do not require accounts and do not provide an email signup form. If you contact the published email address, the email provider may process the address, message, and delivery metadata you choose to send.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Hosting and current analytics state</h2>
      <p>
        The site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may process request metadata such as IP address, user agent, URL, and security signals to deliver and protect the site. No separate analytics script is included in the current site build.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Future advertising cookies</h2>
      <p>No advertising script or ad unit is included in the current site build. If third-party advertising services are added later, this policy and the site's consent controls must be updated before those services load. Third-party vendors, including Google, may then use cookies, web beacons, IP addresses, or similar identifiers to serve and measure ads.</p>
      <p>You can control or opt out of personalized Google advertising through <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/">Google Ads Settings</a>. Additional industry opt-out choices are available at <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/">aboutads.info</a>.</p>
      <p>Google explains how it uses information from partner sites and apps on its <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites">partner-sites data page</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
      <p>
        Outbound retailer links may include affiliate or sponsored tracking parameters. Those third-party sites have their own privacy policies and may collect information after you leave No Lock-In Printer.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="article-section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Privacy questions can be sent to <EmailLink user="hello" domain="nolockinprinter.com" />.
      </p>
    </section>
    <p>Last updated July 11, 2026.</p>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
